%N A259502 Primes p such that nextprime(p + 1)^(p - 1) == 1 (mod p^2).
%C A259502 Nextprime as defined in A007918.
%C A259502 These are Wieferich primes p to a prime base q where the difference between p and q has minimal or almost minimal (if the difference between p and the previous prime is smaller) value.
%C A259502 No further terms up to 10^9.
%o A259502 (PARI) forprime(p=1, , if(Mod(nextprime(p+1), p^2)^(p-1)==1, print1(p, ", ")))
